              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For measurements at filtered beam:",
                "Thicknesses of Ta and In samples are 100 micro-m and",
                "650 micro-m correspondingly. The diameters of tantalum",
                "foil sample and In foil sample were the same and equal",
                "to 28.2 mm. The 115In(n,g)116mIn reaction was used for",
                "monitoring an absolute value of neutron flux.",
                "For measurements at 2.85 and 14.34 MeV:",
                "Thicknesses of Ta samples were 400 micro-m, diameters",
                "equal to 13, 14, and 18.5 mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
